WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'A2Zee' is a Workbench game where the goal is to put a row of
letters in an alphabetical order.

  To play, just click on a tile containing a letter you want to
move and click on the tile where you want to place that letter.
At that moment, the two letters will switch position.

  To complicate matters a little, each time you move some letters,
the letters located on either side of the ones to be moved will
change their position, as shown in the following example:

  CGADEFBH
   ^    ^
   letters to be moved

The result:

  ABCDEHGF
   ^    ^
   moved letters

  Try to put all the letters in the correct order, in the least
amount of moves.

  You can choose to play with as few as 8 letters up to all the
letters of the alphabet (hence the name of the game: A to Z...).

  Have fun!

